{"Title":"麻辣鸡腿的做法","Primary":["鸡腿1个"],"Auxiliary":["食盐适量","酱油适量","醋适量","鸡精适量","葱适量","姜适量","水淀粉适量","调和油适量","芝麻油适量","白糖适量"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.鸡腿洗净去骨","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/e01d3e0b379e80038b19e9a66009ed80.jpg","2.切成小块","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/e1d30911d2ac48e9830446190320e6f1.jpg","3.将鸡肉放进容器内，加少许盐、水淀粉抓匀，再加少许油抓匀，腌渍一会","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/5998c325b67bee89b25113f4c1078f98.jpg","4.干红辣椒和花椒粒稍微用水泡软，这样比较好切","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/bc5aecf9a129d7454154bbeb8fd1cf5b.jpg","5.再将花椒粒和干红辣椒切碎备用","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/28424d7fd46e098b7a7267025df00681.jpg","6.将酱油、醋、白糖、盐、葱姜、香油调成料汁备用","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/e85448e0b492798a9d958f0574658831.jpg","7.热油锅，放入鸡肉翻炒","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/69fd8d7b693fdf421540bda95b86aafd.jpg","8.鸡肉变白后加辣椒花椒粒碎炒出香味","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/7493e1b7dfaa071f3960e94b5d3ea6f4.jpg","9.倒入调好的料汁继续翻炒","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/1f06d25179f97463bab185c1c1f2950a.jpg","10.大火继续翻炒","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/3f931b9074c8a79d7dc0a0063c92905e.jpg","11.炒至汤汁收干即可出锅","[image]:http://images.meishij.net/p/20120920/37bc9d06211735c5bc159bd4b48bc644.jpg"]}